        <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The only ethical requirement in writing is to be absolutely accurate.  —— Ezra Pound&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;about-this-blog&#34;&gt;About This Blog
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The blog covers a range of topics, including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Artificial Intelligence: Theory, derivations, implementations, and applications
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Machine (Statistical) Learning, Deep Learning, Reinforcement Learning, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MLOps, DevOps, Prompt Engineering, RAG, and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The joys of programming&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical writing techniques, standards, and insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Concept analysis and in-depth explanations of various topics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why write?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Treat writing as a method&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;interesting_challenges&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;explain_simply&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;():&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;master&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;review_and_practice&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ask the right questions and aim for progress every day — even just by 1%.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;about-me&#34;&gt;About Me
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m an algorithm engineer specializing in NLP and recommendation systems, currently based in Beijing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Believe in a few things:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Programming is a craft&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engineers are formidable characters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automation is the key to professional happiness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Breadth often leads to depth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;hellip;&amp;hellip;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Great Master title is still far away, Technical Expert has not been achieved, depth is still diving&amp;hellip;&amp;hellip; Haha, another day full of hope.&lt;/p&gt;
